{"tid":1292913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家要清楚局勢要睇台灣明居正既面書而不是陳雲","createTime":"2019-07-07T13:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T23:22:03.000Z","uid":71160,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9b0303152d4c2ca046881a37b427542126013691","tid":1292913,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T13:49:29.000Z","msg":"滲透國際媒體中共無所不在<br />\n-<br />\n收買媒體與記者<br />\n中共想到的是，我買到一個間諜了<br />\n他們是這樣看的，他們的思路跟我們不一樣的<br />\n爭奪文宣陣地，這是一場戰爭<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ppe1ZYSCw9g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dppe1ZYSCw9g&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=ae24161b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ppe1ZYSCw9g</a>"},{"pid":"0d61f20c08522d394249b1aa94c68881e0a463f5","tid":1292913,"uid":71160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T13:50:07.000Z","msg":"反送中讓香港社會開始分裂？！<br />\n<br />\n最後是信任感的問題，中共要自己問問自己，怎麼會搞到大家這麼不相信你？你到底幹了什麼事？不管習近平是否中計，還是你自己想做這事，至少它是不聰明的。<br />\n<br />\n這一次把一些台灣人嚇醒了，往後的發展就是港台會通氣，不一定會真的聯合行動，但港台的聲氣已經開始相通。所以問題會越來變越大，到了後面要怎麼收拾？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JJBeGrBCNus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJJBeGrBCNus&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=4828d55d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JJBeGrBCNus</a>"},{"pid":"9dea3e28dad8d6e0da6f25e210e21ce95a0245e2","tid":1292913,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T13:51:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"120e514c5105357272478a178ef23df5894d74eb","tid":1292913,"uid":25601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:03:58.000Z","msg":"有睇開 佢係第一 二個講中共 習既情況最準既人"},{"pid":"9f6d81a2179586f2e3fb0fd3f6182582e2754704","tid":1292913,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:11:05.000Z","msg":"想了解中共派系鬥爭一定要聽明居正"},{"pid":"8cc